# Default-deny: third-party OSS clones (langchain, llama-index, langchain4j,
# spring-ai-examples, etc.) are gitignored — each developer clones them
# locally for breadth-scan validation. They drift across versions and
# would bloat the repo (~1.8 GB).
*

# Explicit allowlist for AgentShield's own synthetic regression-target
# projects. These are hand-authored as known-answer fixtures for the
# rule pack and MUST be tracked in version control.
!.gitignore
!smartsdk-lambda/
!smartsdk-lambda/**
!synthetic-vuln-java-app/
!synthetic-vuln-java-app/**
!synthetic-vuln-python-app/
!synthetic-vuln-python-app/**
